<%-include("homeModal.ejs") %>

<section class="info-section justify-content-center">
  <h1 class="mb-5 d-flex justify-content-center">Today I Asked Myself</h1>
  <div class="question d-flex justify-content-center mb-5">
    <img src="/assets/quotes.svg" alt="quote" width="25px">
    <span class="mx-4 align-self-center mt-3s">
      <%=question %>
    </span>
    <img src="/assets/quotes-end.svg" alt="end quote" width="25px">
  </div>
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-self-center">
    <button class="start-journal-btn p-2 px-3 shadow-lg rounded-2" data-bs-toggle="modal"
      data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop">
      Start Journaling
    </button>
  </div>

  <main class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap">
    <div class="motto text-center">
      <span>Daily question for a more thoughtful life</span>
      <div class="motto-svg">
        <%-include("mottoSVG.ejs") %>
      </div>
    </div>
     <div class="d-flex mt-4 new-time-discover mb-4 w-75">
        <div class="d-flex column gap-3"> 
            <img src="/assets/newquestions.svg" alt="new questions" width="65px">
            <p class="d-inline">New questions everyday, tailored to you</p>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex column gap-3">
            <img src="/assets/time.svg" alt="time restricted" width="65px">
            <p class="d-inline">Time restricted, editing open only for the first 24hrs</p>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex column gap-3">
            <img src="/assets/discover.svg" alt="discover" width="65px">
            <p class="d-inline">Discover publicly shared journal entries, or share your own</p>
        </div>    
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="draw-animation">
      <div class="rwrs d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap shadow-sm">
        <div data-draw-line="" class="text-draw card-header w-inline-block">
          <p class="text-draw__p fw-bold mt-2">Read</p>
          <div data-draw-line-box="" class="text-draw__box"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-center">Discover how others have answered, understanding the struggles of others helps us to better understand ourselves,
          what would you tell them? And how would that differ to what you would tell yourself?
        </div>
          <img src="/assets/read.svg" alt="read" width="65px" class="align-self-center">
      </div>
      <div class="rwrs d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap shadow-sm">
        <div data-draw-line="" class="text-draw card-header w-inline-block">
          <p class="text-draw__p fw-bold mt-2">Write</p>
          <div data-draw-line-box="" class="text-draw__box"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-center col">Taking just a few minutes to write each day can boost clarity, reduce stress, and spark creativity. 
          Your journal is your space, be brief or dive deep, reflect on your day, or capture passing thoughts.</div>
          <img src="/assets/write.svg" alt="write" width="65px" class="align-self-center">
      </div>
      <div class="rwrs d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap shadow-sm">
        <div data-draw-line="" class="text-draw card-header w-inline-block">
          <p class="text-draw__p fw-bold mt-2">Reflect</p>
          <div data-draw-line-box="" class="text-draw__box"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-center"> use the daily question as a way to dig deep and understand yourself better.
          You have the answers within yourself, you just have to ask yourself the right questions.
        </div>
          <img src="/assets/reflect.svg" alt="reflect" width="65px" class="align-self-center">
      </div>
      <div class="rwrs d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap shadow-sm">
        <div data-draw-line="" class="text-draw card-header w-inline-block">
          <p class="text-draw__p fw-bold mt-2">Share</p>
          <div data-draw-line-box="" class="text-draw__box"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body text-center">Keep your daily answer private or share with others, 
          and invite them to consider how theyâ€™d answer.</div>
          <img src="/assets/share.svg" alt="share" width="65px" class="align-self-center">
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>
</section>